Splitwise App — Design Document

  Overview

  4 flatmates sharing one apartment. Primary loop: add expense → check balance
   → settle up. Secondary: see history, group totals, per-person breakdown.
  Design principle: every common action should take under 5 seconds.

  ---
  Navigation Structure

  Bottom Tabs (mobile) / Top Nav (desktop)
  ├── Home          personal balance, all groups, recent activity
  ├── Groups        groups list → group detail
  └── You           profile, settings

  Add Expense is accessible everywhere via a floating "+" button — not scoped
  to a tab.

