  6. Add Expense — Bottom Sheet → Full Screen

  Trigger: any [＋] button

  This is the most important screen. Two modes: Quick (default) and Advanced
  (user expands).

  Quick mode (default, fits in one screen)

  ┌─── Add Expense ──────── [✕]┐
  │                             │
  │   ₹  [    0.00           ] │  ← large, auto-focused
  │                             │
  │   What for?                 │
  │   [                       ] │
  │                             │
  │   Paid by                   │
  │   [● Mohak (you)        ▾ ] │
  │                             │
  │   Category                  │
  │   [🛒][🏠][⚡][🍕][🚗][📦][+]│
  │                             │
  │   Split between             │
  │   [●Mohak][●Raj][●Priya][●K]│  ← all selected by default
  │   Equal · ₹300 each         │  ← live preview
  │                             │
  │   ﹀ More options            │  ← expands below
  │                             │
  │   [       Add Expense     ] │
  └─────────────────────────────┘

  Expanded "More options"

  │   Split type                │
  │   [Equal ●] [Exact] [%] [÷]│
  │                             │
  │   Date       [Today      ▾]│
  │                             │
  │   Tags       [+ Add tag   ]│
  │                             │
  │   Notes      [             ]│
  │                             │
  │   Recurring  [ ] Off       │

  Split type: Exact

  │   Split between  (₹1,200)  │
  │   ┌───────────────────────┐ │
  │   │ Mohak     [  600.00 ] │ │
  │   │ Raj       [  300.00 ] │ │
  │   │ Priya     [  200.00 ] │ │
  │   │ Karan     [  100.00 ] │ │
  │   └───────────────────────┘ │
  │   ✓ ₹1,200 — fully assigned │  ← live validation

  Split type: Percentage

  │   Mohak     [ 50 ]%  ₹600  │
  │   Raj       [ 25 ]%  ₹300  │
  │   Priya     [ 15 ]%  ₹180  │
  │   Karan     [ 10 ]%  ₹120  │
  │   100% assigned             │

  States:
  - Amount 0 → "Add Expense" button disabled
  - Description empty → button disabled
  - Exact/% split doesn't sum → button disabled, shows "₹X remaining" in red
  - Success → sheet closes, list refreshes, brief toast "Expense added"

  Group pre-selection: If launched from inside a group → group picker is
  hidden and pre-filled. If from Home → show group picker first.

  APIs: POST /groups/:id/expenses, optionally POST
  /groups/:id/expenses/preview (for live split preview)

